<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:150px;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/mlister/mlister_chibi.png" style="width:150px;" alt="mlister_chibi.png" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:150px;">
<p>Recovered material, believed to be a representation of Mlister. Note similarity to work from Zhange.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>So.</p>
<p>Uh,</p>
<p>Hi.</p>
<p>This is my author page. It's kinda weird and meta.</p>
<p>As you might be able to tell, I'm not exactly sure where to take it.</p>
<p>I'll just plonk down my stuff.</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p>Ignore all this awkward white space.</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
